com.ikala.android.bdl.tracking.event

Class EventParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ikala.android.bdl.tracking.event.EventParam

  • public class EventParam
extends Object
    EventParam contains all the keys of Event parameters. You can use these constants as the Bundle key to generate a parameters Bundle for Tracker.addEvent(EventName, Bundle).
    See Also:
    Tracker.addEvent(EventName, Bundle)
